data.description: This charming and spacious home will make you feel like you've stepped back in time. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen, perfect for entertaining friends and family. Beautiful woodwork with large windows that fill the space with abundant natural light. The updated kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage for all your culinary needs. The bedrooms are generously sized and provide a peaceful retreat for rest and relaxation. With multiple bedrooms, there is plenty of space to accommodate a growing family or host overnight guests. Outside, you'll find a well-maintained yard that provides alley access with space for a 4 car garage, perfect for the car enthusiasts!
